---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy" description="Valiant Vineyards cookie policy - how we use cookies on our website.">
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-5xl">
          Cookie Policy
        </h1>

        <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          <p>Effective date: December 05, 2025</p>
          <p>Last updated: December 18, 2025</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 space-y-10">
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground">
              What are cookies?
            </h2>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              <p>
                This Cookie Policy explains what cookies are, how we use them, the types of cookies we use (i.e., the information we collect using cookies and how that information is used), and how to manage your cookie settings.
              </p>
              <p>
                Cookies are small text files used to store small pieces of information. They are stored on your device when a website loads in your browser. These cookies help ensure the website functions properly, enhance security, improve the user experience, and analyze performance to identify what works and where improvements are needed.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground">
              How do we use cookies?
            </h2>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              <p>
                Our website is designed with your privacy in mind. We use only essential cookies that are strictly necessary for the website to function properly and keep our services secure. We do not use cookies for advertising, tracking, or analytics purposes.
              </p>
              <p>
                For analytics, we use Cloudflare Web Analytics, which is a privacy-focused analytics service that does not use cookies or collect any personal data. It provides us with aggregate, anonymous insights about how visitors use our website without tracking individuals.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground">
              Types of cookies we use
            </h2>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              <p>
                <strong>Essential/Security Cookies:</strong> These cookies are set by Cloudflare to help protect our website from malicious traffic and ensure the security of your connection. They are strictly necessary for the operation of our website.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground">
              Managing cookies
            </h2>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              <p>
                Since we only use essential cookies required for security and basic functionality, there is no consent banner or preference center on our website. However, you can still manage cookies through your browser settings.
              </p>
              <p>
                Different browsers offer various methods to block and delete cookies. Below are links to support documents on how to manage cookies in major web browsers:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>
                  <a href="https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/32050" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gold hover:underline">Chrome</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a href="https://support.apple.com/en-in/guide/safari/sfri11471/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gold hover:underline">Safari</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/clear-cookies-and-site-data-firefox" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gold hover:underline">Firefox</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/delete-cookies-in-microsoft-edge-63947406-40ac-c3b8-57b9-2a946a29ae09" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gold hover:underline">Microsoft Edge</a>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                Please note that blocking essential cookies may impact the functionality of our website.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
